query:
SELECT 
  isTest, 
  status, 
  COUNT(*) as count,
  MIN(createdAt) as earliest,
  MAX(createdAt) as latest
FROM webhook_logs 
WHERE createdAt > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR)
GROUP BY isTest, status
